import "./index.scss";
import LoginPage from "../components/LoginPage"
import WindowLayout from "../components/WindowLayout"

const login = (username, password, session) => {
  alert(`${username} ${password} ${session}`)
  session.user = username
  session = Object.assign(session, {user: username})
}

const Index = ({ session }) => <WindowLayout height="380px" width="380px" logo>
  <LoginPage session={session} login={login}/>
</WindowLayout>

export default Index
